"authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 14, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-14 10:28", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "国算到底是怎么才能亏的？[del]黑人问号脸[/del][s:ac:咦]", "lou": 2010, "content_length": 39, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776133689}, {"pid": 864512467, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 56, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-14 10:35", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "商业航天这边我也帮你们排除了一个最近唯一有可能出问题的天银  最高点附近跑路的<br/>商航又是怎么能亏的？<br/><br/>然后三个材料  鼎龙新阳南大  哪个能亏？<br/>铜箔2个  哪个能亏？<br/>电子布更不用说了<br/>长线电池更是连调整都没有<br/>设备ETF最近也是没事的<br/><br/>你们到底怎么亏的？<br/>4000以上该小心是真的 但是说亏到底是怎么亏的。", "lou": 2011, "content_length": 268, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776134109}, {"pid": 864513280, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 15, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-14 10:40", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "这里就是高的卖掉 换那种没涨的机构票  跳水和你们有什么关系", "lou": 2012, "content_length": 54, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776134407}, {"pid": 864513800, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 15, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-14 10:43", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864513626,45974302,3736]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=38534514]晨星233[/uid] (2026-04-14 10:42):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，材料换设备，这个思路对吗？[s:ac:茶][/quote]<br/>我最近喜欢材料 是很喜欢的那种", "lou": 2013, "content_length": 33, "reply_to": 864513626, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776134595}, {"pid": 864514107, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 15, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-14 10:45", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864513934,45974302,3737]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=32483780]Sunnyabuse[/uid] (2026-04-14 10:44):[/b]<br/><br/>没涨的机构票，你一定在说xwtx[img]https://img.nga.178.com/attachments/mon_202009/01/9bQ5-9huuKiToS46-3m.png[/img][/quote]<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202604/14/jmQ2x-3ep8K8T1kSd1-1i.jpg[/img]<br/>我的是这个<br/>这个也是空X材料<br/>拿这种低位的 刚才跳水和我有什么关系", "lou": 2014, "content_length": 101, "attachs": [{"attachurl": "mon_202604/14/jmQ2x-3ep8K8T1kSd1-1i.jpg", "size": 9, "type": "img", "subid": 0, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202604/14", "name": "jmQ2x-3ep8K8T1kSd1-1i.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "56"}], "reply_to": 864513934, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776134703}, {"pid": 864514771, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 16, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-14 10:49", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864514060,45974302,3737]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67121932]黄金大人[/uid] (2026-04-14 10:44):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大 固态能当长线做吗[/quote]<br/>我买的第一秒就说这个方向是长线 而且说了逻辑 甚至还暴露了一个票", "lou": 2015, "content_length": 65, "reply_to": 864514060, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776134956}, {"pid": 864516198, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 13, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-14 10:58", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864515913,45974302,3739]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67143775]plicro[/uid] (2026-04-14 10:56):[/b]<br/><br/>现在感觉已经到了没人不相信不涨的情况？<br/>那这一波以机构自救为引导的报团光等等的情况<br/>后续还需要国家队吗[/quote]<br/>只有国家队才有普涨<br/>机构只会结构性抱团。", "lou": 2016, "content_length": 43, "reply_to": 864515913, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776135484}, {"pid": 864516646, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 47, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-14 11:00", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864516210,45974302,3739]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67157410]c471167449[/uid] (2026-04-14 10:58):[/b]<br/><br/>没有亏，这反弹我都觉得强度有点离谱了，这几天就反弹了30多个点，各种新高，强度有限强的。。[/quote]<br/>机构结构性抱团自救 所以我说这里是机构最舒适的区域<br/>用了几个票就探出来了<br/>全市场应该只有我第一个判断出来是机构自救行情", "lou": 2017, "content_length": 117, "reply_to": 864516210, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776135638}, {"pid": 864519324, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 29, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-14 11:16", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864518948,45974302,3741]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67157410]c471167449[/uid] (2026-04-14 11:14):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大我发现机构做票也是轮着做的，先拿他的活动仓先拉他手里的1板块，自救完了出货去做2板块，然后去3、4、5，这样子，等指数阶段见顶或者出现减仓信号了，他们就一把全减了。[s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/>对啊  不然我为什么说不断高切低<br/>这才是自救啊", "lou": 2018, "content_length": 45, "reply_to": 864518948, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776136584}, {"pid": 864529902, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 26, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-14 12:25", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864529678,45974302,3748]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66746361]come1200[/uid] (2026-04-14 12:24):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，这个机构也差不多自救完了，后面还是按照之前的等5浪下跌抄底吗？[/quote]<br/>哪就自救完了 不还是在不断轮动么<br/>到时候看有没有新资金来  如果没有 就双底 如果有  就短C", "lou": 2019, "content_length": 82, "reply_to": 864529678, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776140730}], "__T": {"fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "topic_misc": null, "subject": "自立自强，科学技术打头阵", "locked": 0, "recommend": 0, "quote_to": null, "quote_from": 0, "type": 36, "replies": 155489, "authorid": 150058, "postdate": 1768179906, "lastpost": 1782109303, "jdata": null, "author": "-阿狼-", "lastposter": "异乡猫", "digest": 0, "lastmodify": 1782109315, "tpid": 0, "post_misc_var": {"content_length": 412, "fid": 706, "comment_id": ",854270755,860174433", "14": {"17": 1, "14": 4, "13": 4, "12": 1}, "16": "63335896,19412700,26652007,67067074,20672033,66881586,67068843,66199622,60819388,60409766,67057614,60264977,61082281,42701832,66998841,61574956,61272875,67082978,66949654,65530601,60630412,60240136,66038632,63481990,61973100,60192597,66985104,19043499,39108806,41714633,7046671,65647302,40696141,3481707,654677,39235785,66063392,3931479